OL,3,CMan 'bombarded' police with sexual
OL,4,Cphone calls
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after
OL,7,F"bombarding" a police control room
OL,8,Fwith inappropriate calls and sexual
OL,9,Fcomments.
OL,11,FBetween 18 and 19 October 2023, Mark
OL,12,FClayton made 19 calls to South
OL,13,FYorkshire Police without any reason
OL,14,Fother than to discuss his sex life and
OL,15,Fmake false allegations.
OL,17,FThe 59-year-old pleaded not guilty to
OL,18,Fthe charge of sending an offensive,
OL,19,Findecent, obscene, or menacing message
OL,20,Fby a public communication network and
OL,21,Fbreaching a restraining order.
