OL,6,FAfter failing to appear at Sheffield
OL,7,FCrown Court, Clayton, of Periwood
OL,8,FLane, Sheffield, was found guilty in
OL,9,Fhis absence.
OL,11,FHe was sentenced at Sheffield
OL,12,FMagistrates Court to 18 weeks in
OL,13,Fprison, ordered to pay a #154 victim
OL,14,Fsurcharge, #300 to cover costs and
OL,15,Fhanded a Criminal Behaviour Order for
OL,16,Ftwo years.
