OL,3,CMan 'bombarded' police with sexual
OL,4,Cphone calls
OL,6,FPC Paul Brunt said: "Clayton's actions
OL,7,Ftook valuable time away from our call
OL,8,Fhandlers who should have been
OL,9,Fassisting people experiencing genuine
OL,10,Femergencies.
OL,12,F"Our staff carry out a high pressure
OL,13,Fjob often helping people in their
OL,14,Fdarkest hour and treating them with
OL,15,Fthis lack of respect is shocking.
OL,17,F"I hope this result sends a strong
OL,18,Fmessage to those thinking of making
OL,19,Fprank calls to the police."
